-		 * CPU 0                             CPU 1
-		 * <loop receiver>
-		 *   smp_rmb(); (A) <-- pair -.      <waker thread>
-		 *   <load ->r_msg>           |        msr->r_msg = NULL;
-		 *                            |        wake_up_process();
-		 * <continue>                 `------> smp_wmb(); (B)
-		 *                                     msr->r_msg = msg;
-		 *
-		 * Where (A) orders the message value read and where (B) orders
